sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Ingestor
    participant Index as BM25 Index
    participant FS as File System

    note over Ingestor: Initialization
    Ingestor->>FS: Scan *.md files
    FS-->>Ingestor: Return file paths
    loop For each file
        Ingestor->>Ingestor: Read & Chunk Text (Paragraphs)
    end
    Ingestor->>Index: Build Token Index
    
    note over User: Query Time
    User->>Index: "How does the Repository work?"
    Index-->>Index: Calculate Relevance Scores
    Index-->>User: Return Top 3 Chunks
